OL,3,COxford United confirm head coach has
OL,4,Cleft the club
OL,6,FOxford United have confirmed that head
OL,7,Fcoach has left the club after only six
OL,8,Fmonths in charge.
OL,10,FThe former Wycombe boss replaced Gary
OL,11,FRowett in January but was unable to
OL,12,Fkeep the U's in the Championship, as
OL,13,Fthey were relegated to League One.
OL,15,FDespite an upturn in form, Oxford were
OL,16,Frelegated to the third tier in 22nd
OL,17,Fplace
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
