OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782037091
OL,3,COxford United confirm head coach has
OL,4,Cleft the club
OL,6,FHe was unbeaten in his first three
OL,7,Fgames, with 2 draws and a win, but the
OL,8,Fteam struggled in February and were
OL,9,Fultimately relegated.
OL,11,FThe search for a new head coach begins
OL,12,Fimmediately, say the club as it
OL,13,Fsearches for its fourth manager in
OL,14,Funder two years.
OL,16,FFixtures for the new EFL season are to
OL,17,Fbe released on Thursday, June 25.
OL,19,FOxford said Bloomfield had
OL,20,F"represented Oxford United with
OL,21,Fprofessionalism and integrity."
