OL,3,COxford United confirm head coach has
OL,4,Cleft the club
OL,6,FAn Oxford United spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We would like to thank Matt for his
OL,8,Fefforts and wish him every success in
OL,9,Fthe future.
OL,11,F"The process of appointing a new Men's
OL,12,FFirst Team Head Coach will begin
OL,13,Fimmediately, and the Club will provide
OL,14,Fupdates in due course."
